  <thing id="fS2Fulmina" name="Fulminate" description="You explode.\n\n{b}Prerequisites:{/b} 2 HD, undead type, corporeal body.\n\n{b}Benefit:{/b} When you are reduced to 10 or fewer hit points, you explode. You deal 1d6 fire damage per 2 HD in a 30 ft. radius. Creatures and objects in this radius may make a Reflex save (DC 10 + 1/2 your HD + your Cha modifier) for half damage. If your pieces aren&apos;t found and destroyed (dealt damage equal to your remaining hit points), your corpse reforms in 2d12 hours." compset="Feat" summary="When you are reduced to 10 or fewer hp, you explode." uniqueness="useronce">
