  <thing id="fS2ShadMin" name="Shadow Minion" description="You can send your shadow out to do your bidding.\n\n{b}Prerequisite:{/b} 7 HD, undead type, Cha 13.\n\n{b}Benefit:{/b} As a standard action,  you can detach your shadow and have it act as your loyal agent. Your shadow acts as a shadow (the undead creature) totally loyal to you, with HD equal to the level of the cohort you would receive if you had the Leadership feat (see below and PFRPG Core Rulebook, p.129). Your shadow can reattach itself to you as a swift action, and is immune to all damage and all effects while acting as your normal shadow. It heals itself of hp equal to your HD for every 24 hours it remains attached to you. If your shadow is destroyed, you have no shadow for 30 days, after which it returns and can once again be sent out.\n\nLeadership score: total levels &amp; HD + Cha modifier\nScore --&gt; Cohort level\n2 --&gt; 1\n3 --&gt; 2\n4-5 --&gt; 3\n6 --&gt; 4\n7-8 --&gt; 5\n9 --&gt; 6\n10-11 --&gt; 7\n12 --&gt; 8\n13 --&gt; 9\n14-15 --&gt; 10\n16 --&gt; 11\n17-18 --&gt; 12\n19 --&gt; 13\n20 --&gt; 14\n21-22 --&gt; 15\n23 --&gt; 16\n24+ --&gt; 17" compset="Feat" summary="You can send your shadow out to do your bidding." uniqueness="useronce">
    <comment>From SGG - 7 Feats for the Undead</comment>
    <usesource source="srcAoW"/>
    <tag group="Helper" tag="NoPathSoc"/>
