    <exprreq message="Must be undead."><![CDATA[#hastype[tpUndead] <> 0]]></exprreq>
    </thing>
  <thing id="fS2MistWlk" name="Mist Walk" description="You can often get ahead of your prey, even if you always seem to be moving slowly.\n\n{b}Prerequisites:{/b} 12 HD, undead type, incorporeal or gaseous form.\n\n{b}Benefit:{/b} You gain the ability to travel between darkness and shadow as if by means of a {i}dimension door{/i} spell. The limitation is that the magical transport must begin and end in an area with no more than dim light. You can teleport up to a total of twice your movement rate as a standard action, or up to four times your movement rate as a full round action." compset="Feat" summary="You can often get ahead of your prey, even if you always seem to be moving slowly." uniqueness="useronce">
