  <thing id="tmS2FavKyu" name="Favored Spawn of Kyuss" description="&quot;Favored Spawn of Kyuss&quot; (known simply as the &quot;favored&quot; to cultists of Kyuss) is an inherited template that can be added to any living, corporeal creature. A favored spawn uses all the base creature&apos;s statistics and special abilities except as noted here.\n\n{b}Special Qualities:{/b} A favored spawn retains all the special qualities of the base creature and gains the following.\n{b}Damage Reduction (Ex):{/b} A favored spawn of Kyuss gains damage reduction 5/silver. If the favored spawn has 10 or more Hit Dice, this increases to damage reduction 10/silver.\n{b}Fast Healing (Ex):{/b} A favored spawn of Kyuss has fast healing 5.\n{b}Turn Resistance (Ex):{/b} A favored spawn of Kyuss has channel resistance +3.\n{b}Abilities:{/b} Increase from the base creature as follows: Str +4, Int +2, Wis +2, Cha +2. Favored spawn are undead and as such do not have a Constitution score.\n{b}Feats:{/b} A favored spawn of Kyuss gains Improved Unarmed Strike as a bonus feat.\n{b}Challenge Rating:{/b} +2 (for creatures with 9 HD or less) or +3 (for creatures with 10 HD or more).\n{b}Alignment:{/b} Always chaotic evil." compset="Template" uniqueness="unique">
