  <thing id="rcS2InfeSk" name="Infested Skin" description="The favored spawn of Kyuss is so infested with worms that any creature that strikes it with an unarmed strike, natural weapon, or light weapon must make a Reflex save or a Kyuss worm is transferred to the attacker&apos;s body. Any creature that shares the same square as the favored spawn (such as might occur during a grapple, bull rush, or Acrobtics check) must make a Reflex save to avoid the same fate." compset="RaceCustom" summary="Close contact requires a Reflex save to prevent a worm transfering to the attacker." uniqueness="useronce">
