  <thing id="raS2ImmMin" name="Immunity to Mind-Affecting Effects" description="Because its alien mind functions differently than those of other creatures, a spell weaver is immune to all mind-affecting spells and effects." compset="RaceSpec" summary="Immune to all mind-affecting spells and effects.">
